.controls.hidden
  %h1#roll-output
    \-
  %button#roll-button 
    Roll
  %ul.players

.new-game
  .row
    .content.large-8.columns.offset-2
      .large-8.columns#rules
        %h1.title
          PokeBooze
        %h3 
          Gotta Drink 'Em All
        %p
          Welcome to the digitized Pokemon Drinking Game v2.0, now even easier to play; just 
          %strong hit spacebar to roll.
          We'll move the pieces, you just read the instructions where you land... wouldn't want to make it too easy ;).
        %p
          %strong If you've never played: 
          the aim of the game is simple, get to the end before your friends, and try not to pass out along the way.
        %p.footnote
          PS: We didn't make the board itself, as awesome as it is. Legend has it some guy named 
          %a{href: "http://www.funnyjunk.com/funny_pictures/3509756/Pokemon+Drinking+Game+Version+2.0/"} raith
          did.

      .large-4.columns#players
        %h2
          New Game
        %P
          Enter the names of each drinker.
        %form#players-input
          %input.player-input{type: "text", placeholder: "Player 1's Name"}
          %input.player-input.hidden{type: "text", placeholder: "Name"}

        %button#start-game
          Lets Get Drunk!

